snippet.title: Tako no Himitsu: Ocean of Secrets - Kickstarter Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Tako no Himitsu: Ocean of Secrets is launching on Kickstarter Today!
Support the game here:  https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1373467035/tako-no-himitsu-ocean-of-secrets?ref=51fk5l

From the developers of Save me Mr Tako comes Tako no Himitsu: Ocean of Secrets, a new ARPG set in a world consumed by the shadows of its past. Join six heroes and embark on an adventure to try and save it!

A public demo is available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2357380/Tako_no_Himitsu_Ocean_of_Secrets/

A Game by Deneos, music by Marc-Antoine Archier and Motoi Sakuraba
